<br>
The purpose of this forum would be for direct communication among guilds without interference/flames from junior members of their guilds or even those not affiliated but who can't resist butting into the business of others.<br>
<br>
Some examples are:<br>
<br>
1)  guildmember_01 training guards/mobs onto unsuspecting victims in the name of RP<br>
2)  members of guild_01 camping a high-demand mob 24/7 for days on end<br>
3)  guildofficer_01 asking tips/advice on how to better serve their particular guild or run their website<br>
4)  warn each other about bugs and exploits (like the trade window hack)<br>
<br>
<br>
It would be nice to have a single forum dedicated to mature, serious thinking for the more important issues.<br>
<br>
Well, that's my two coppers worth.<br>
